Sure, here are some examples of using the word "beri" in Serbian with translations in English:

1. *Beri* jagode iz bašte. (Pick strawberries from the garden.)
2. *Bere* jabuke na plantaži. (He/she is picking apples on the plantation.)
3. *Braća* beru grožđe u vinogradu. (The brothers are picking grapes in the vineyard.)
4. *Birači* biraju nove predstavnike u izborima. (Voters are choosing new representatives in the elections.)
5. *Berem* iskustva iz svakodnevnog života. (I am harvesting experiences from everyday life.)
6. *Berači* duvana sakupljaju listove na polju. (Tobacco pickers are collecting leaves in the field.)
7. *Bereš* poslednje plodove u vrtu. (You are picking the last fruits in the garden.)
8. *Biraj* boje koje ti se sviđaju. (Choose the colors that you like.)
9. *Berući* pečurke, našao sam otrovnu gljivu. (While picking mushrooms, I found a poisonous one.)
10. *Birao* je najbolje rešenje za svoj problem. (He was choosing the best solution for his problem.)

I hope this helps!